Butterflies Space Rescue: Earth Chronicles

Introduction: The Butterfly Space Rescue team‚Äîa group of skilled alien explorers‚Äîhas received a mission from the "Butterfly Space Rescue GLOBE Team Organization." They are tasked with exploring Earth to uncover secrets of its unique environment, collect data, and report their findings to GLOBE.gov. Equipped with advanced technologies and specialized skills, each member must work collaboratively to explore the mysteries of Earth's ecosystems.

