Failure (Dice Roll ‚â§ 3): A sudden storm causes the team to seek shelter, and they miss the chance to gather critical information. The mission must be rescheduled.
Choice B: Collect Soil Samples

Success (Coin Flip Heads): The Guardians of the Cocoon Kingdom successfully gather soil samples, revealing high levels of moisture and nutrients. This data is reported and used for further analysis.
Failure (Coin Flip Tails): The soil samples are contaminated during collection. The Quantum Butterflies must use their skills to clean up the area, delaying the mission.
Scenario 2: The Lunar Link

Mission Objective: Moon Explorers must travel to a mysterious crater on the Moon believed to hold minerals that can benefit Earth‚Äôs ecosystem. They need to study the minerals and bring back samples.

Choice A: Mining Lunar Minerals

Success (Dice Roll ‚â• 5): The Moon Explorers collect rare minerals that, when analyzed by Quantum Butterflies, show potential to improve crop growth on Earth.
Failure (Dice Roll ‚â§ 4): The mining equipment malfunctions, and they must call for assistance from Crystal Moths to navigate back safely.
